    "body": "Hi @FabienMotte ,\n\nThanks for your quick response but I am not sure about that createInstanceSearchRoute is only compatible with SSR because we have working filters with this method, I can make a demo that you see it's working.\n\nI think the expected behavior is the sever return the static search and in the client is checked the query params to load the correct page or filters if isn't the default.\n\nThanks",
