    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @RodrigoTomeES,\r\n\r\nThanks for your message. It's great to hear that you've been able to use the `createInstanceSearchRoute()` function with filters even without SSR. However, I wanted to clarify that our routing system is based on query parameters, and `getStaticProps()` doesn't provide query parameters out of the box (https://github.com/vercel/next.js/discussions/17269). While it may be possible to work around this limitation in custom ways, we don't officially support such approaches. I updated our documentation to clarify the support of `getStaticProps()`.\r\n\r\nIf you have any further questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to reach out.",
