    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi @FabienMotte ,\r\n\r\nWe don't have customice nothing, with filters just work you can see it in the demo that I made. Look:\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13077343/236157531-5489b78e-f674-4e77-9886-31627d4aeac7.mov\r\n\r\n\r\nMaybe this behavior is a bug but for every one that use routing with SSG is a great feature! Because we have the server state that return the default state an algolia read the parameters an load the current filters requested in client if needed.\r\n\r\nThanks\r\n",
